body:
I check opponents,every time i finish a game.I saw a lot of bronze 1-5 players with 300+ mastery points,and 3x level 7 masteries on some &#039;hard to master champs&#039;

If they are stuck in bronze,what can i expect as someone who has 70 pvp games in total (30 ranked and around 50 non ranked)?

I know i should not be looking it that way,but its really big letdown at least to me seeing people like that stuck in bronze.They must have at least some knowledge of this game,and how champions works,and then you have me,who has only one champ at level 6 mastery,and 47 mastery score in total,trying to improve.
